Class Booking

java.lang.Object
com.inFlight.shared.model.Booking
public class Booking extends Object
Booking is a class that represents a booking made by a passenger. It contains information about the booking ID, passenger ID, slot ID, tier, and status. POJO (Plain Old Java Object) class.
